<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="NMT15">
<l>palatēva rēttap paṭikaṭantāṉ pāta</l>
<l>malarēṟa viṭṭiṟaiñci vāḻtta valarākil</l>
<l>mārkkaṇṭaṉ kaṇṭa vakaiyē varuṅkaṇṭīr</l>
<l>nīrkkaṇṭaṉ kaṇṭa nilai</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>If [you] are able to offer numerous blossoms, bow down at, and praise</l>
<l>the feet of Him who stepped over the earth so that many gods praised,</l>
<l>the very means [through which] Mārkaṇḍeya discovered the condition experienced</l>
<l>by the [venomed] liquid-throated [Śiva] will come [to you too], see!</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
